[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man dies after crash between car and van in Claudy

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has died in hospital after he was injured in a car crash in County Londonderry.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 60-year-old was a passenger in a car that was involved in a collision with a van on the Foreglen Road in Claudy at about 16:00 BST on Tuesday.
The injuries sustained by the drivers of the car and the van are not believed to be life-threatening.
Police have appealed for anyone who witnessed the crash to contact them.
